rows.label: tlk70000073_05_msg0001
rows.name:
I have to say, that was some solid
work you did there.

rows.label: tlk70000073_05_msg0002
rows.name:
Figured we'd cave under the pressure,
but no, the people of the capital really
pulled together when they needed to.

rows.label: tlk70000073_05_msg0003
rows.name:
Thanks to that, it got me wondering
how they're doing over at the
resistance camp.

rows.label: tlk70000073_05_msg0004
rows.name:
It was fun while it lasted back there.
Shame I've no reason to go back.

rows.label: tlk70000073_05_msg0005
rows.name:
It's true what they say. You don't know
what you have till you lose it.

rows.label: tlk70000073_05_msg0006
rows.name:
Damn. I knew my life was veering in
the wrong direction. If only I'd been
more sensible...

rows.label: tlk70000073_05_msg0008
rows.name:
Say...when exactly is it too late to turn
your life around again?
